cast.overview: Molly Bloom, a young skier and former Olympic hopeful becomes a successful entrepreneur (and a target of an FBI investigation) when she establishes a high-stakes, international poker game.
cast.title: Molly's Game

details.biography: Bo Martynowska is a Slavic-Canadian artist born on the Baltic island of Uznam 27/09/1991. Martynowska is a graduate of Humber College's Arts program and later majored in Psychology at York University in Toronto. Bo is best known for her role as Temperance Hudson on The CW's Nancy Drew and Tiffany Gimble on Designated Survivor.
details.name: Bo Martynowska
